data.description:
CUSTOM HOME ON HORSE PROPERTY WITH MOUNTAIN VIEWS!! You're not going to want to just drive by this home. Inside you will find a large open
kitchen with double ovens and an under counter built in microwave oven, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, large drawers, reverse osmosis, water
softener, split floor plan, double sinks in both bathrooms, 4 car, climate controlled extended length garage with a 50 amp plug. House is situated at an angle on the property to allow for better Energy Efficiency. Home has R48 insulation. the roof has a built in bird deterrent. 30x30 extra thick concrete pad by the horse stalls to build your custom shop. This custom home is a must see as there is so many upgrades for you to check out! Garage AC is new as of 10/8/2023!
